snippet: Top-seeded Stan Wawrinka hit 49 winners and saved two match points to reach the quarterfinals of the Open 13 in a 6-4, 4-6, 7-6 (8) win over Sergiy Stakhovsky on Wednesday....
lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Stan Wawrinka hit 49 winners and saved two match points to reach the quarterfinals of the Open 13 in a 6-4, 4-6, 7-6 (8) win over Sergiy Stakhovsky on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Wawrinka Saves 2 Match Points to Reach Quarters in Marseille
headline.main: Wawrinka Saves 2 Match Points to Reach Quarters in Marseille
